701546f-a.title: Bronx: Olinville Avenue - Duncomb Street
701546f-a.text:
Intersection of Olinville Avenue (left) and Duncomb Street,
looking south from the Bronx River Parkway.
May 12, 1938.
P. L. Sperr.

701545f-a.text:
